mazon', 'PENGUIN CAFE ORCHESTRA -tribute--Various Artists']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="https://itunes.apple.com/jp/album/penguin-cafe-orchestra-tribute/id260520304?uo=4&at=10lcnA" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'PENGUIN CAFE ORCHESTRA -tribute--Various Artists']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div><div class="music-wrap clear"><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/08/rest-of-the-pieces.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/restpieces.jpg" alt="Rest of the Pieces / Calm" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/08/rest-of-the-pieces.php">Rest of the Pieces<br />Calm</a></h4><p>幻想的な音楽を作り続けるCalm作品のレアトラック集です。ピアノの美しさを感じられるものからグルーヴ感溢れるものまで幅広い選曲となっています。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B001RR1B76?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B001RR1B76" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Rest of the Pieces-Calm']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="https://itunes.apple.com/jp/album/rest-of-the-pieces/id308976386?uo=4&at=10lcnA" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Rest of the Pieces-Calm']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/08/casa-1.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/casa2.jpg" alt="Casa / Morelenbaum2/Sakamoto" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/08/casa-1.php">Casa<br />Morelenbaum2/Sakamoto</a></h4><p>ジョビンのスタジオでジョビンのピアノを使って録音された作品です。美しいブラジルの音楽の真髄を感じることができる名作です。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B00005LK4C?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B00005LK4C" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Casa-Morelenbaum2/Sakamoto']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div><div class="music-wrap clear"><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/08/all-in-one.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/allinone.jpg" alt="All In One / Bebel Gilberto" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/08/all-in-one.php">All In One<br />Bebel Gilberto</a></h4><p>ジョアン・ジルベルトの娘のベベウの作品。伝統的なブラジル音楽とエレクトリックなアプローチを体感できる作品です。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B002LMOCH2?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B002LMOCH2" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'All In One-Bebel Gilberto']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="https://itunes.apple.com/jp/album/all-in-one-bonus-track-version/id332800304?uo=4&at=10lcnA" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'All In One-Bebel Gilberto']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/08/virgin-ubiquity-unreleased-recordings-1976-1981.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/virginubiquity.jpg" alt="Virgin Ubiquity (Unreleased Recordings 1976-1981) / Roy Ayers" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/08/virgin-ubiquity-unreleased-recordings-1976-1981.php">Virgin Ubiquity (Unreleased Recordings 1976-1981)<br />Roy Ayers</a></h4><p>ロイ・エアーズの未発表音源集。クールなグルーヴと心地よいアンサンブルが心を落ち着けてくれる1枚です。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B0000DF687?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B0000DF687" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Virgin Ubiquity (Unreleased Recordings 1976-1981)-Roy Ayers']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fvirgin-ubiquity-unreleased%252Fid5120723%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Virgin Ubiquity (Unreleased Recordings 1976-1981)-Roy Ayers']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div><div class="music-wrap clear"><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/04/music-of-bill-evans.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/musicofbilevans.jpg" alt="Music of Bill Evans / Kronos Quartet" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/04/music-of-bill-evans.php">Music of Bill Evans<br />Kronos Quartet</a></h4><p>ビル・エヴァンスの名曲を弦楽四重奏でプレイした作品。まるで映画のサントラのような雰囲気を持つ作品です。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B0002BO0LM?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B0002BO0LM" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Music of Bill Evans-Kronos Quartet']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="https://itunes.apple.com/jp/album/kronos-quartet-music-bill/id26084282?uo=4&at=10lcnA" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Music of Bill Evans-Kronos Quartet']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div></div>

